this application contains two pages :

1)SignUp.html
2)Regions.html 


functionality : 

make use of the Google Maps API to present the map and regions as Polygon’s

• make use of the Firebase API to access the locations used to define the regions

• create a user programmatically with email/password credentials. During registration, you will

need to gather their first and last name and store it on the Firebase database

• sign in to firebase using email/password credentials that you’ve created

• include a button that can be used to toggle on/off the visibility of the regions

• centre the map on the user’s current location